{"tid":2076179,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蓬佩奧聲援加國 要求北京釋放「人質」","createTime":"2020-06-23T10:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T11:27:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1638a23c44c6d05241648bac3f83e6e17367edb4","tid":2076179,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200623/JVU67QFEBJXXAQ6IGVT35FB2LA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200623%2FJVU67QFEBJXXAQ6IGVT35FB2LA%2F&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4JW5pKsuoI6OgBDFn4N8w%2Bso%3D&h=f5b45b76\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200623%2FJVU67QFEBJXXAQ6IGVT35FB2LA%2F&h=52f9ac60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200623/JVU67QFEBJXXAQ6IGVT35FB2LA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧聲援加國 要求北京釋放「人質」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AIDMRLLK4CJY3CQTFA6FW6GMXE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAIDMRLLK4CJY3CQTFA6FW6GMXE.jpg&h=2386dc60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中方拘留斯帕沃和康明凱500多天後起訴二人，被外界斥為「人質外交」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n加拿大公民康明凱（Michael Kovrig）和斯帕沃（Michael Spavor）被中國拘留逾550天後，上周被中國以間諜罪起訴。美國國務卿蓬佩奧周一發聲明聲援加拿大，批評中國的決定是出於政治動機而且「完全沒有根據」，要求北京立即釋放兩人。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧在聲明中表示，美國「與加拿大並肩」，要求北京立即釋放兩人，抵制中方「使用這些不合理的拘留手段威迫加拿大」，斥有關指控出於政治動機而且「完全沒有根據」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥起訴出於政治動機<br />\n<br />\n他同時呼籲加拿大根據《維也納領事關係公約》的要求，讓領事立即接觸兩名公民，因為中國已禁止有關..................................知道這兩名加拿大人的狀況。<br />\n<br />\n此外，中歐領導人周一以視像方式舉行會面，歐洲理事會主席米............................................瑞典公民是誰，外界相信他是指香港銅鑼灣書店前股東桂民海。<br />\n<br />\n中方上周五以間諜罪起訴康明凱及斯帕沃後，加拿大總理杜魯對此表示失望，揚言將繼續向中方施壓，令兩人早日獲釋。中國外交部發言人趙立堅昨在例行記者會不點名批評杜魯多，..............................<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院/路透社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3ZEZOG2U5MUTXSGVK3TK23KAHY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3ZEZOG2U5MUTXSGVK3TK23KAHY.jpg&h=c35f560e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蓬佩奧"},{"pid":"ee73710f4223c2d447f30363a3623a02a7087d43","tid":2076179,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bae47ca63c0cea03bba18196311d5da00fbeb0d","tid":2076179,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:49:51.000Z","msg":"流氓就係咁<br />\n泊車仔想做大佬想到傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3e426be9b1e7af630ceb7504256db39d8585b7","tid":2076179,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"同美加玩人質外交<br />\n不如數下支那有幾多人質同錢係佢地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘玩玩下俾美國做埋回血劍"},{"pid":"b1ba766a863f5e6dd002fbdf9ef61c23ccb07745","tid":2076179,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba3e426be9b1e7af630ceb7504256db39d8585b7","tid":2076179,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:53:40.000Z","msg":"同美加玩人質外交<br />\n不如數下支那有幾多人質同錢係佢地身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分分鐘玩玩下俾美國做埋回血劍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T10:59:43.000Z","msg":"佢就係睇死美加唔會做到佢咁盡<br />\n人地講法治，佢就莫須有"},{"pid":"9b6f794d84cad0ca006fc7f7c9241aa39c17198a","tid":2076179,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1ba766a863f5e6dd002fbdf9ef61c23ccb07745","tid":2076179,"uid":60508,"like":0,"dislike":0